const bodyHtml = "<main><div class=\"site-shell article-layout\"><article class=\"article\"><a class=\"article-meta\" href=\"/guides#months-list\">2026-03-23 • Farming</a><h1>Pest Farming Guide for Hypixel SkyBlock in 2026</h1><p class=\"lede\">Pest farming is what happens when ordinary Garden progression turns into a specialized route. The method is not just \"farming with extra drops.\" Current creator coverage makes clear that once you center the setup around pests, your farm layout, armor, pet logic and overall expectations all change. That shift matters because pest farming can become extremely strong, but only when treated as its own system instead of a side bonus stapled onto a normal crop routine.</p><div class=\"note\"><strong>Primary source base:</strong> current pest-farming creator testing, especially around Helenthis armor, pest chance, plot management and realistic route setup. <a href=\"/guides/farming-progression-guide-2026\">Read the farming progression guide first</a> if your Garden foundation is not built yet.</div><h2>Pest farming begins with controlled conditions</h2><p>The most useful advice in the current pest-farming material is structural: the route depends on building for pest generation and cleanup, not simply harvesting the crop you like most. That means plot decisions matter, traffic through the farm matters and gear choices matter in a way that basic early Garden play does not. Players who jump in without restructuring often end up with a setup that is technically pest-capable but not actually efficient enough to justify the attention.</p><p>This is why specialized equipment like Helenthis armor gets so much discussion. Pest farming pays players who lean into the dedicated loop. If you half-build the method, you often inherit the setup cost without getting the corresponding consistency. That is a recurring pattern across SkyBlock money methods: specialization only shines once the specialization is real.</p><h2>Do not confuse showcase numbers with baseline results</h2><p>Pest farming content often includes flashy money numbers, but the stable takeaway is more conservative. The route becomes strong when your Garden foundation is already solid and you are ready to commit to the branch. It is not usually the first farming page a player should copy. That is why this guide comes after the broader farming progression article. You need the Garden base first, then the pest branch. Reversing that order usually leads to overspending and disappointment.</p><p>Use the live tools to watch prices of both crops and pest-related outputs in real time. <a href=\"https://bazaartracker.com/demand\">BazaarTracker demand</a> shows whether buyers are still clearing pest drops at instant-buy speed, <a href=\"https://sky.coflnet.com/topMovers\">SkyCofl top movers</a> catches Helenthis-tier mat swings as they happen, <a href=\"https://sky.coflnet.com/bazaar\">SkyCofl bazaar</a> tracks median price and spread, and <a href=\"https://skyblock.bz/\">Skyblock.bz</a> ranks the farming product family by 24h movement. Pest farming is unusually sensitive to whether the surrounding market still rewards the extra complexity. When prices and ROI are healthy, the route outperforms simple harvesting. When they cool off, the specialized setup deserves a harder look.</p><h2>Read next</h2><ul class=\"related-list\"><li><a href=\"/guides/farming-progression-guide-2026\">Farming Progression Guide for Hypixel SkyBlock in 2026</a></li><li><a href=\"/guides/melon-vs-wheat-farming\">Melon vs Wheat Farming Economics</a></li><li><a href=\"/guides/first-50m-coins-guide\">Your First 50M Coins in Hypixel SkyBlock</a></li></ul></article><aside class=\"article-aside\"><div><h3>Best paired tools</h3><ul class=\"tool-list\"><li><a href=\"https://bazaartracker.com/demand\">BazaarTracker demand</a></li><li><a href=\"https://bazaartracker.com/margin\">BazaarTracker margin</a></li><li><a href=\"https://sky.coflnet.com/topMovers\">SkyCofl top movers</a></li><li><a href=\"https://sky.coflnet.com/bazaar\">SkyCofl bazaar</a></li><li><a href=\"https://skyblock.bz/\">Skyblock.bz trends</a></li><li><a href=\"https://pro.skyblock.bz/features/bazaar-flipping\">BazaarPro bazaar flipping</a></li></ul></div><div><h3>Best for</h3><p>Players with an established Garden who want to branch into a more specialized and actively managed farming route.</p></div><div><h3>Source videos</h3><p>The best pest coverage focuses on setup rules and realism rather than pretending every player will match top showcase numbers immediately.</p></div></aside></div></main>";
